---
import { Button } from "@/components/ui/button";
---

<section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-12">
      <div class="lg:w-1/2">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-[#0D2845]">About Us</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Let's talk to the friendly team about how to bring your life's dreams into focus. As one of the Northeast's premier client-centered wealth management and financial planning firms, we understand that everyone's situation is unique.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Since 1995, we have been providing comprehensive financial planning services to help our clients achieve their goals. Our team of experienced professionals is dedicated to delivering personalized solutions that align with your values and objectives.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <Button class="bg-[#156F89] hover:bg-[#125d73]">Meet Our Team</Button>
          <Button variant="outline" class="border-[#156F89] text-[#156F89] hover:bg-[#156F89] hover:text-white">
            Learn More
          </Button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="lg:w-1/2">
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600880292203-757bb62b4baf?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80"
          alt="Financial advisors in a meeting"
          class="rounded-lg shadow-xl w-full"
          width="600"
          height="400"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>